  "general_provisions": "This bill modifies provisions related to energy rebate programs.",
  "hilighted_provisions": "This bill:<hr><ltbullet>defines terms;<hr><ltbullet>requires a large-scale public utility to operate an energy rebate program;<hr><ltbullet>requires a large-scale public utility to annually report to the Office of Energy Development regarding the large-scale public utility's energy rebate program; and<hr><ltbullet>modifies the Office of Energy Development's reporting duties to include a review of energy rebate programs.",
